						<AuditIssue>IT Investments - How does the organization manage IT investments?</AuditIssue>
						<Criteria>
							<cri>
								<tx l="eng" name="Organizations should manage their IT projects and investments in manner that maximizes benefits and considers elements such as risk, capabilities, needs, and prioritization among competing investments."/>
