						<ak>Management of various services that support the business in a manner that
keeps up with the demands of the business or users. In order to manage capacity the IT organization needs to measure current conditions and needs to take action that facilitates providing users with additional capacity, for example by acquiring additional processing power when certain parameters are crossed.</ak>
					</narr>
