		<Domain nr="03">
			<title>
				<tx l="eng" name="Development and Acquisition"/>
				<tx l="alb" name="Zhvillimin dhe Blerjet"/>
			</title>
			<Narrative>
				<narr l="eng">
					<ak>In order to support the business strategy, IT organizations provide solutions to the business or business user. The process of developing, acquiring, or contracting out for a solution should be planned so that risks can be managed and chances of success are maximized.</ak>
