			<Area nr="01">
				<title>
					<tx l="eng" name="Requirements Development and Management"/>
					<tx l="alb" name="Zhvillimi dhe menaxhimi i kërkesave"/>
				</title>
				<Narrative>
					<narr l="eng">
						<ak>For any project development or acquisition the organization needs to document the requirements of what they want and to manage those requirements. Managing requirements includes prioritizing them utilizing adopted criteria (for example criticality, cost, and complexity) and segmenting them into phases if they all cannot be implemented in one initial system.</ak>
					</narr>
				</Narrative>
