			<Area nr="05">
				<title>
					<tx l="eng" name="Overseas Service Provider"/>
					<tx l="alb" name="Ofruesit e huaj të shërbimeve "/>
				</title>
				<Narrative>
					<narr l="eng">
						<ak>Employing overseas service provider is a common form of outsourcing, especially in a cloud computing environment. In this scenario, the risks to such outsourcing would involve foreign regulations on information storage and transfer may limit what can be stored and how it can be processed, data may be used by law enforcement of foreign country without the knowledge of the organisation, privacy and security standards may not always be commensurate and disputes because of the different legal jurisdiction cannot be totally avoided.</ak>
					</narr>
				</Narrative>
				<Issue nr="01" RiskWeight="1" Include="No" Remarks="xPre-Assessment: Domain - Low;  Area - Low; ">
