							</obj>
						</Objectives>
						<AuditIssue>Have all the costs (including future costs) for outsourcing identified? Has due cost benefit analysis been carried out and best option been chosen? Are there specific responsibilities on the organization in the outsourcing and do they have critical cost elements/ impacts built in? Are additional costs or escalated costs being charged to the agency?</AuditIssue>
						<Criteria>
							<cri>
								<tx l="eng" name="The cost benefit analysis is realistic and is the basis to which the program is managed and controlled"/>
