			<Area nr="02">
				<title>
					<tx l="eng" name="Establishment of Business Continuity Function"/>
					<tx l="alb" name="Struktura e Funksionit të Vazhdimësisë së Biznesit"/>
				</title>
				<Narrative>
					<narr l="eng">
						<ak>The business continuity management team must be organised to represent all appropriate
business functions. Senior management and other related officials must support a continuity program and be associated with the process of developing the policy.</ak>
					</narr>
				</Narrative>
